                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290910-286-off1575 t18290910-286-crimeloc1578"></join>, where my wife <rs id="t18290910-286-viclabel1579" type="occupation">keeps a shop</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290910-286-victim2680 t18290910-286-viclabel1579"></join>. The prisoner and another man came there with each a basket, on the 6th of August - the prisoner asked for some half-boots to look at, and then said he would come again; the other man then said he would come again - my wife said to the prisoner."Where are those I showed you?" he said, "You put them into the glass case:" I said to him, "Let me look into your basket;" he set off and ran - I pursued; he dropped the basket, and it contained these boots; I took them up, and a neighbour stopped him - I gave him in charge.</p>
